      ~ Change dice to d6
      #value2[rcPUaRngAt] = 6

      ~ Set the "Active Energy Type" on to the ranged attack pick
      perform hero.pulltags[PsiActEne.?]
      perform hero.childfound[rcPUaRngAt].pushtags[PsiActEne.?]]]>
